- Green rectangular block: **Index 6** (Use once in each structure)
- Yellow vertical rectangular block: **Index 11** (Use twice on left)
- Blue cube block: **Index 3** (Use once on right)
- Orange triangular prism roof block: **Index 16** (Use once on right)
